libibmad
------------------------------------------
libibmad provides low layer IB functions for use by the IB diagnostic and
management programs. These include MAD, SA, SMP, and other basic IB functions.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libibmad-devel-1.3.13-1bl2
  libibmad5-1.3.13-1bl2
  libibumad3-1.3.10.2-1bl3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libibumad-devel-1.3.10.2-1bl3
  libtool-2.5.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://www.openfabrics.org/

Canonical download:
  https://www.openfabrics.org/downloads/management/libibmad-1.3.13.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libibmad-1.3.13-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libibmad-1.3.13-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libibmad-1.3.13-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libibmad-1.3.13-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libibmad5-1.3.13-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libibmad-devel-1.3.13-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libibmad)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libibmad.README
  /usr/share/doc/libibmad/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libibmad/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libibmad/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libibmad/README

(libibmad5)
  /usr/bin/cygibmad-5.dll

(libibmad-devel)
  /usr/include/infiniband/mad.h
  /usr/include/infiniband/mad_osd.h
  /usr/lib/libibmad.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libibmad.pc

